extendedInfo.description: Read The Football League NEWS for The Championship,League One,and League Two- npower Championship news, including for each team- npower League 1 news, including for each team- npower League 2 news, , including for each team- npower Football League Info. Championship, League 1, League 2 Scores. Championship, League 1, League 2 Fixture. Championship, League 1, League 2 Table. Championship, League 1, League 2 Top Scorers. Championship, League 1, League 2 transfer~ Favorite/share by long-press item/news items~ Search and play video, including Championship, League 1, League 2, Highlights, Goals, Playoff. This function need YoutuBe player on device.Please enjoy The Football League News
